title: "Sonic the Hedgehog 3"
rating: 7.3
review {
  direction {
    director {
      name: "Jeff Fowler"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The direction on a macroscale is pretty fun, as it creates this gaming action-comedy that is pretty true to the Sonic games; The direction on a microscale is decent, as it has the silly comedy moments Sonic is known for and tackles some darker, more mature themes that you do not see as much in a family movie; The storytelling is what you would expect from a family movie"
  }
