      comments: "Plays the gritty nature of Shadow well;  Basically, it\'s just John Wick, but Shadow"
    }
    cast {
      rating: "Decent"
      comments: "Typical family movie background character performances help with establishing the tone and making the movie silly fun"
    }
    rating: "Decent to Pretty Good"
  }
  story {
    writer {
      name: "Pat Casey"
    }
    writer {
      name: "Josh Miller"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The concept is a continuation of the Sonic the Hedgehog story, with the added Shadow storyline that is true to the video games, particularly \"Sonic Adventure 2\"; the plot structure is pretty simple; character writing captures the essence of these characters that is true to the video games"
  }
  screenplay {
    writer {
      name: "Pat Casey"
    }
    writer {
      name: "Josh Miller"
    }
    writer {
      name: "John Whittington"
    }
    rating: "Decent to Pretty Good"
    comments: "The dialogue is pretty and family-oriented, but does get a little mature at points; The humor is very silly and meta, so it\'s what you would expect from both Sonic the Hedgehog and Jim Carrey; The symbolism is somewhat present as the movie touches on familial themes and loss; The foreshadowing is pretty standard because you kind of expect where this movie is going because it\'s made for families"
  }
  score {
    composer {
      name: "Tom Holkenborg"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "It helps establish the tone and does a decent job incorporating classic Sonic themes"
  }
  soundtrack {
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Enjoyed how they included \"Live and Learn\" as an homage to \"Sonic Adventure 2\""
  }
  cinematography {
    cinematographer {
      name: "Brandon Trost"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Standard for an action-comedy of this scale;"
  }
  editing {
    editor {
      name: "Al LeVine"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "Pretty sound;"
  }
  sound {
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "Helped make the action-comedy what it is"
  }
  visual_effects {
    rating: "Good"
    comments: "Helped mesh the Sonic characters with the environment as the overall feel makes the movie look like it is in the Sonic universe"
  }
  costumes {
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "Helps make the Roboniks look like their video game characters;"
  }
  pacing: "Pacing is a little on the faster side; but there really isn\'t that much plot to go through"
  climax: "Climax is pretty cool as it pays homage to \"Sonic Adventure 2\""
  tone: "Tone is silly, family comedy that makes this feel like it\'s something from the Sonic franchise;"
  final_notes: "Really enjoyed the homages to the Sonic franchise and *Sonic Adventure 2*;"
  overall: "Overall, a pretty good family comedy that is carried by its silly humor, action sequences, and performances from Jim Carrey, Ben Schwartz, Idris Elba, and Keanu Reeves; I also really enjoyed how the movie drew a lot of inspiration from one of the franchise's best games, \"Sonic Adventure 2\""
